In [4]:
plots = [bokeh.plotting.figure(plot_width=900, plot_height=300, title=None, x_range=(3.5, 7.36), y_range=(-5_000_000, 95_000_000), x_axis_label='retention time', y_axis_label='counts') for i in range(3)]

for p in plots:
    p.outline_line_color = None
    p.output_backend='svg'
    p.xgrid.grid_line_color = None
    p.ygrid.grid_line_color = None

color_pal = {'alone':bokeh.palettes.viridis(3)[2], '5_locc':bokeh.palettes.viridis(3)[0], '5_locc_glued':bokeh.palettes.viridis(3)[1]}
index = {'alone':0, '5_locc':1, '5_locc_glued':2}
legend = {'alone':'single bug alone', '5_locc': 'bug with 5 L. occidentale ants', '5_locc_glued': 'bug with 5 L. occidentale ants, glued mandibles'}

for f, c in zip(metadata.loc[metadata['SPME_total_time']>1500]['s_file'], metadata.loc[metadata['SPME_total_time']>1500]['interactor']):
    file = f
    df = pd.DataFrame(pyteomics.mzxml.read(file))
    df_chromat = pd.DataFrame({'chromat': np.array([np.sum(val) for val in df['intensity array'].values]), 'num': df['num'].values, 't': df['retentionTime']})
    df_chromat.loc[(df_chromat['t']>4.55) & (df_chromat['t']<4.70)] = np.nan

    plots[index[c]].line(df_chromat['t'], df_chromat['chromat'], color=color_pal[c], line_width=2, legend_label=legend[c])

bokeh.io.show(bokeh.layouts.gridplot(plots, ncols=1))
